	<chapter id="logmanager_dependency">
		<title>Dependency</title>
		<para>
			사용자 Application을 Anyframe Log Manager와 연동하기 위해서는 MongoDB-Driver, Anyframe Log Manager등의 
			Dependency를 추가해주도록 한다. 
		</para>
		<informaltable>
			<caption>Anyframe Log Manager와 연동하기 위한 Dependency</caption>
			<tgroup cols="4">
				<colspec colnum="1" colname="col1" colwidth="6*" />
				<colspec colnum="2" colname="col2" colwidth="3*" />
				<colspec colnum="3" colname="col3" colwidth="1*" />
				<thead>
					<row>
						<entry align="center">Name</entry>
						<entry align="center">Version</entry>
						<entry align="center">Required</entry>
					</row>
				</thead>
				<tbody>
					<row>
						<entry align="center">mongo-java-driver.jar</entry>
						<entry align="center">2.10.1</entry>
						<entry align="center">Y</entry>
					</row>
					<row>
						<entry align="center">anyframe-logmanager.jar</entry>
						<entry align="center">1.1.1-SNAPSHOT</entry>
						<entry align="center">Y</entry>
					</row>
				</tbody>
			</tgroup>
		</informaltable>
		<para>Maven 기반의 프로젝트로 생성할 경우 아래와 같이 pom.xml에 Dependency를 추가해 주도록 한다. </para>
		<programlisting language="xml"><![CDATA[<dependency>
  <groupId>org.mongodb</groupId>
  <artifactId>mongo-java-driver</artifactId>
  <version>2.10.1</version>
</dependency>
<dependency>
  <groupId>org.anyframe</groupId>
  <artifactId>anyframe-logmanager</artifactId>
  <version>1.1.1-SNAPSHOT</version>
</dependency>]]></programlisting>
	</chapter>